# AUDIT-FIX Q19 (2026-05-17): Claude Code git worktrees — local-only,
# never to be committed. Each worktree is a full source-tree copy used
# by parallel subagent sessions. Previously the root `.worktrees/`
# pattern caught a non-existent path; the actual location is nested
# under `.claude/`. Excluding both for belt-and-suspenders.
.claude/worktrees/

